				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$r^{-1}$\end{document} of the plasma density was observed (Galand et al. 2016), as predicted by the model (see Fig. 29). Fig. 30
